            <span id="First_Paragraph_Mod">
            The missionaries made appointments to give discussions to me every day that next week. They came and on one of the days, they said, “By the way, Sister Roos, we have a baptism set up for the 17th of July. Would you like to be baptized on that day?”
            <br />
            </span>
            <div id="boxmodex3" class="clearfix">
                <div class="ChapterVideoDivMod">
